{"id":206,"date":"2017-02-11T11:15:55","date_gmt":"2017-02-11T11:15:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=206"},"modified":"2020-03-13T17:08:28","modified_gmt":"2020-03-13T17:08:28","slug":"add-currencies-in-total-to-words-feature","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/add-currencies-in-total-to-words-feature\/","title":{"rendered":"Add currencies in total to words feature"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>If you are using total to words in your transactions you need to add the currency words manually into the translation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Perfex comes with 2 predefined currency names who are already added into the converter. If you added your own currency you need to add this also to&nbsp;total to words converter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You need to add your currency database name and the currency string who will be output inside\u00a0the invoice\/estimate.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"745\" height=\"184\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/total-to-word-invoice-currency.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-207\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/total-to-word-invoice-currency.png 745w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/total-to-word-invoice-currency-300x74.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/total-to-word-invoice-currency-60x15.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/total-to-word-invoice-currency-150x37.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In this example we will add British Pound to the converter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a file with name <a href=\"https:\/\/www.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/my_functions_helper.zip\"><strong>my_functions_helper.php<\/strong><\/a> in\u00a0application\/helpers\/ and add the following code:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">function add_total_to_words_currency($currencies){\n    $currencies['GBP'] = 'British Pounds';\n\n    return $currencies;\n}\n\nhooks()->add_filter('before_number_format_render_languge_currencies','add_total_to_words_currency');\n<\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Note that the GBP is the same as the name we have set up inside the CRM (showed in the image);<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you are using total to words in your transactions you need to add the currency words manually into the translation. Perfex comes with 2 predefined currency names who are already added into the converter. If you added your own currency you need to add this also to&nbsp;total to words converter. You need to add [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[20,16,22],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-206","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-general","category-sales","category-customization"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/206","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=206"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/206\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=206"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=206"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.p